values:
she just&nbsp;
does it
with hope&nbsp;in her fingertips&nbsp;
or too much love&nbsp;
in her heart she is able&nbsp;
to touch and heal her hurting loves

she is amazing and everything&nbsp;
i am not

.........

I wish I could trade places with my brother. My heart longs for his physical&nbsp;freedom but I am at least thankful&nbsp;that I'm watching his spirit be freed by his growing knowledge of God. Fridays are good but hard at the end. Almost too hard.

I can't get along with my mother and it bothers me but what I don't know what else to do.&nbsp;

I got a promotion at work.

Changes are brewing. In me and in my circumstances.

I wonder if in the end I'll be alright.&nbsp;

I am a waster of many things
but mostly how I miss the people I've pushed away.

The Lord takes pity on me and is gracious and&nbsp;
I would be dead without his love.&nbsp;

Thats all I know tonight..
